display_long_description:
Street Simulator Z: Multiplayer is an addictive VR sandbox where you can get rich through legally questionable means, spend your money on new weapons and vehicles, and avoid the cops while battling the local gang. Take on the streets solo or team up with others in multiplayer (up to 4 players).

[media]

Make money your way: grow exotic “tomatoes”,sell them to locals, and reinvest to expand your business. Become a bounty hunter and take down criminals for cash, or just rob the local bank.


Spend your wealth on new weapons and a wide variety of vehicles—from a tractor to even a tank.

Key Features:

🤝 Co-op multiplayer (up to 4 players)

⚔️ Interact with any NPC, go to war with gangs, and evade the police

🍅 Grow and sell “tomatoes” for cash, then reinvest to expand your business and increase profits

💰 Spend your money on a variety of weapons and vehicles
